lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur teenager Dele Alli scored a contender for goal of the season when he lifted the ball over his head, swivelled past a defender and volleyed home as they won 3-1 at Crystal Palace in the Premier League on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Both Managers Praise Alli's Stunning Spurs Goal
